# Ticket shuffle minigame



Four-ticket quadrant shuffle that picks between two movie candidates.



## Entry flow



1. `armTicketShuffle` — preview / arm the shuffle button

2. `launchTicketShuffle` — runs cinematic intro and shuffle sequence

3. `onShuffleTicketPick` — user selects the winning ticket



Shared setup with coin toss: `canStartTicketShuffle`, `buildFilteredCoinTossPool`, filter gates (runtime, decade, watched).



## Timing constants



All shuffle timing lives in `SHUFFLE_*` constants (~lines 2545–2612):



- Swap/spin/feint durations: `SHUFFLE_SWAP_MS`, `SHUFFLE_SPIN_MS`, `SHUFFLE_FEINT_MS`, etc.

- Layout positions: `SHUFFLE_QUADRANT_SLOTS`, `SHUFFLE_ROW_SLOTS`, `SHUFFLE_CONFIRM_*`



Change existing constants — do not introduce inline magic numbers elsewhere.



## Audio



- UI clip paths from `window.uiAudioPaths` (source: `scripts/audio-paths.mjs`)

- Golden ticket playback rate: `shuffle-golden-ticket-map.js` (regenerated by `npm run refresh-audio`)

- After path changes in `scripts/audio-paths.mjs`, run `npm run refresh-audio`



## Styles



Shuffle arena and ticket animations are in `app/style.css`. Match existing neon/arcade ticket aesthetic when adding classes.
